♪ ♪

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:45.000
Wow.

01:13:48.000 --> 01:13:49.000
Hors d’oeuvres, sir?

01:13:49.000 --> 01:13:50.000
Good evening.

01:13:50.000 --> 01:13:52.000
No, thank you.
No, thanks.

01:13:52.000 --> 01:13:53.000
Do you want some?

01:13:55.000 --> 01:13:58.000
Not nervous, are you?
Doctors.

01:13:58.000 --> 01:14:00.000
Kind of a stuffy crowd,
but nice.

01:14:00.000 --> 01:14:02.000
Sure.

01:14:04.000 --> 01:14:06.000
MAN 1:
You know, he hired
a personal trainer.

01:14:06.000 --> 01:14:08.000
MAN 2:
Oh, yeah,
heard that.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:09.000
Hey, thanks for
coming with me.

01:14:09.000 --> 01:14:11.000
Thank you.

01:14:11.000 --> 01:14:14.000
Jake! I see they got you here.

01:14:14.000 --> 01:14:15.000
Feldman.

01:14:15.000 --> 01:14:17.000
Hello.

01:14:17.000 --> 01:14:20.000
Oh, I’m sorry.
You haven’t met.

01:14:20.000 --> 01:14:21.000
Um, Dr. Feldman,

01:14:21.000 --> 01:14:22.000
this is Leah.

01:14:23.000 --> 01:14:26.000
Is this one your wife?

01:14:28.000 --> 01:14:32.000
Yes, this is Leah.
My wife Leah.

01:14:38.000 --> 01:14:39.000
Hello.

01:14:50.000 --> 01:14:52.000
LEAH:
Not much.

01:14:52.000 --> 01:14:53.000
I’m gonna take
the SATs soon.

01:14:53.000 --> 01:14:55.000
So how are
your studies going?

01:14:55.000 --> 01:14:58.000
Jake told Raj that
he’s been helping you.

01:14:58.000 --> 01:14:59.000
I think that’s sweet.

01:14:59.000 --> 01:15:02.000
Oh, he’s been a lifesaver.

01:15:02.000 --> 01:15:04.000
Looks like the fellows
are moving up in this world

01:15:04.000 --> 01:15:06.000
to get invited
to this.

01:15:06.000 --> 01:15:09.000
Hi, Carol. Carter.

01:15:11.000 --> 01:15:15.000
This is Leah.

01:15:15.000 --> 01:15:17.000
Carter Weston,
renal transplant.

01:15:21.000 --> 01:15:22.000
It’s nice
to meet you...

01:15:22.000 --> 01:15:23.000
both.

01:15:23.000 --> 01:15:24.000
You guys are

01:15:24.000 --> 01:15:26.000
so tan!
Where you been?

01:15:27.000 --> 01:15:28.000
Jamaica.
Away for few days.

01:15:28.000 --> 01:15:30.000
(piano playing light melody)

01:15:33.000 --> 01:15:35.000
Carter, I love this song.

01:15:37.000 --> 01:15:39.000
Nice to meet you, Leah.

01:15:44.000 --> 01:15:46.000
Raj, ask me to dance.

01:15:46.000 --> 01:15:48.000
To this? I-I can’t
dance to this.

01:15:48.000 --> 01:15:50.000
Lucky for us
you won’t be tempted

01:15:50.000 --> 01:15:52.000
to make any of your
breakout moves.

01:15:52.000 --> 01:15:53.000
You do work with
these people. Come on.

01:15:53.000 --> 01:15:56.000
(Raj clears throat)

01:16:00.000 --> 01:16:01.000
Carter can dance.

