01:23:14.000 --> 01:23:16.000
I’m sorry.

01:23:16.000 --> 01:23:17.000
Excuse me.

01:23:32.000 --> 01:23:33.000
Hey.

01:23:41.000 --> 01:23:44.000
What’s wrong?

01:23:44.000 --> 01:23:46.000
I don’t want to talk about it.

01:23:46.000 --> 01:23:48.000
Is it me?

01:23:48.000 --> 01:23:50.000
No.

01:23:52.000 --> 01:23:54.000
It’s us. It’s...

01:23:54.000 --> 01:23:56.000
it’s these.

01:23:57.000 --> 01:23:58.000
Our letters.

01:24:01.000 --> 01:24:03.000
I feel like I’m betraying Ben.

01:24:03.000 --> 01:24:04.000
I mean, you
were his wife.

01:24:04.000 --> 01:24:05.000
Don’t you feel guilty?

01:24:10.000 --> 01:24:12.000
No.

01:24:15.000 --> 01:24:17.000
I love you.

01:24:18.000 --> 01:24:21.000
That’s what I feel.

01:24:21.000 --> 01:24:23.000
Did you love him?

01:24:36.000 --> 01:24:39.000
Our marriage wasn’t
set up like that.

01:24:39.000 --> 01:24:42.000
I was 18.

01:24:42.000 --> 01:24:45.000
Your brother

01:24:45.000 --> 01:24:48.000
was a good man.

01:24:48.000 --> 01:24:50.000
He was very serious,

01:24:50.000 --> 01:24:53.000
dedicated...

01:24:53.000 --> 01:24:58.000
but there was something
missing between us.

01:25:00.000 --> 01:25:03.000
You didn’t answer my question.

01:25:03.000 --> 01:25:04.000
Did you love him?

01:25:06.000 --> 01:25:08.000
You know, I didn’t plan
this would happen between us.

01:25:08.000 --> 01:25:11.000
I gotta go.

01:25:26.000 --> 01:25:28.000
(sighs)

01:25:28.000 --> 01:25:30.000
(phone ringing)

01:25:51.000 --> 01:25:54.000
I don’t know what to do.

01:25:54.000 --> 01:25:56.000
Dude, it was so much easier
when you dated non-relatives.

01:25:58.000 --> 01:25:59.000
Sorry.

01:26:01.000 --> 01:26:05.000
Look, man, maybe you’re
looking at this all wrong.

01:26:05.000 --> 01:26:08.000
Maybe the brother you
shunned all those years

01:26:08.000 --> 01:26:09.000
is actually looking
out for you.

01:26:25.000 --> 01:26:26.000
